    "Simultaneously, it is of high importance to analyze network activity patterns to understand and identify coordinated inauthentic behavior.",
    "This analysis will provide a foundation for targeted interventions and astroturfing detection mechanisms.",
    "Policy recommendations for social media platforms can be developed to enforce stricter measures against coordinated inauthentic behaviors, enhancing the overall integrity of the information ecosystem.",
